    <p><b><i>Dept. of Electrical Engineering, IIT-Delhi</i></b>, Delhi, India on Change Detection Algorithms in computer vision.  <i>(October 2010-January 2011)</i><br>
      Change detection algorithms using segmentation and defocussing. Implemented using open-source computer vision libraries on a smart camera system. </p>

    <p><b><i>Infinera India Private Ltd.</i></b>, Bangalore, India in hardware team on system verification.  <i> (January 2010-June 2010)</i> <br>
      Board simulation and system level testing of a system of line cards. Implemented a basic Verilog parser for netlist parsing and verification.</p>

    <p> <b><i>Vikram Sarabhai Space Center (VSSC)</i></b>, Thiruvananthapuram, India on testing of control module electronics.<i>(May 2008-July 2008) (Summer intern)</i> <br>
      Interfaced and programmed a PIC microcontroller to generate waveforms for testing control electronics module and mechanical characteristics of an electro-mechanical system.</p>

